[SPEAKER_01] I took the question from your mouth.

747
01:05:42,199 --> 01:05:45,519
[SPEAKER_01] Because you can imagine, people ask me that all the time.

748
01:05:45,519 --> 01:05:54,099
[SPEAKER_01] And my poor husband, I love him so dearly because he loves me so much.

749
