[SPEAKER_01] I'm very, I've always, I was always very proud and I lacked a lot of humility.

750
01:06:00,539 --> 01:06:04,960
[SPEAKER_01] And I was always very strong-willed.

751
01:06:04,960 --> 01:06:08,699
[SPEAKER_01] And I think part of that is because I always had to depend on myself.

752
01:06:08,699 --> 01:06:12,659
[SPEAKER_01] I didn't know how to depend on anyone else.

753
01:06:13,199 --> 01:06:15,739
[SPEAKER_01] And the men in my life had always failed me.

754
01:06:15,739 --> 01:06:20,380
[SPEAKER_01] And I was with this wonderful man who loved me.

755
01:06:20,380 --> 01:06:23,860
[SPEAKER_01] And I didn't know how to trust him in that way.

756
01:06:23,860 --> 01:06:26,880
[SPEAKER_01] To just depend on him and rely on him.

757
01:06:26,880 --> 01:06:30,099
