760
01:06:35,019 --> 01:06:36,340
[SPEAKER_01] The whole time.

761
01:06:37,079 --> 01:06:39,400
[SPEAKER_01] The whole time, he said, I don't understand.

762
01:06:39,400 --> 01:06:40,559
[SPEAKER_01] Just quit your job.

763
01:06:40,559 --> 01:06:43,619
[SPEAKER_01] And I thought, what do you mean you don't understand, you know?

764
01:06:43,619 --> 01:06:46,039
[SPEAKER_01] What are we going to do about this?

765
01:06:46,039 --> 01:06:47,900
[SPEAKER_01] How are we going to pay the house?

766
01:06:47,900 --> 01:06:49,139
[SPEAKER_01] And how are we going to pay this?

767
01:06:49,139 --> 01:06:53,059
[SPEAKER_01] And, you know, I'm like, do you not understand that there's, we have a budget.

768
01:06:53,059 --> 01:06:54,460
[SPEAKER_01] We have bills to pay.

769
01:06:54,460 --> 01:06:55,039
[SPEAKER_01] We have a budget.

770
01:06:55,039 --> 01:06:57,099
[SPEAKER_01] And what are we going to do without my income?

771
01:06:57,099 --> 01:06:58,539
[SPEAKER_01] And he said, just quit.

772
01:06:58,539 --> 01:06:59,500
[SPEAKER_01] We'll be okay.

773
01:07:00,139 --> 01:07:01,860
[SPEAKER_01] And I thought, no, I can't.

774
