779
01:07:19,440 --> 01:07:21,940
[SPEAKER_01] And nothing else was spoken.

780
01:07:21,940 --> 01:07:22,940
[SPEAKER_01] Just tears.

781
01:07:23,280 --> 01:07:34,079
[SPEAKER_01] And then when I went back to work the following day, I just, I felt this heaviness, you know, of now this sense of urgency.

782
01:07:34,079 --> 01:07:35,059
