783
01:07:35,059 --> 01:07:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] I don't know when that's going to be.

784
01:07:36,659 --> 01:07:39,579
[SPEAKER_01] I have to find another job quickly.

785
01:07:39,579 --> 01:07:45,679
[SPEAKER_01] I wasn't finding anything, which is incredible because normally I would, was able to find a job very easily.

786
01:07:45,679 --> 01:07:47,159
[SPEAKER_01] But it wasn't happening.

787
01:07:48,159 --> 01:07:53,400
[SPEAKER_01] So I went back to Mass the following Sunday, which was the first Sunday after Easter.

788
01:07:53,400 --> 01:07:55,880
