840
01:12:26,199 --> 01:12:29,460
[SPEAKER_01] And so I was calling all the women to reschedule them.

841
01:12:29,460 --> 01:12:32,920
[SPEAKER_01] And I didn't have to see anybody.

842
01:12:32,920 --> 01:12:35,159
[SPEAKER_01] I didn't sell any contraception.

843
01:12:35,159 --> 01:12:46,420
[SPEAKER_01] And on the third day of the week, so on Friday, on May the 6th of 2011, so I'll celebrate 14 years this May 6th since I left Planned Parenthood.

844
01:12:46,420 --> 01:12:57,420
[SPEAKER_01] But on that Friday, I was probably about an hour away from walking out of Planned Parenthood when a woman came in for a pregnancy test.

845
01:12:57,420 --> 01:13:06,680
[SPEAKER_01] And on the intake form, it asks the question, you know, if your pregnancy test is positive, you know, what type of referral would you like?

846
01:13:06,680 --> 01:13:11,359
[SPEAKER_01] And she had checked the box abortion, adoption, and prenatal care.

847
01:13:11,840 --> 01:13:13,819
[SPEAKER_01] So she marked, checked all three boxes.

848
01:13:13,819 --> 01:13:21,020
[SPEAKER_01] And usually in the past, when women would check all three boxes, it usually meant that they wanted an abortion.

849
01:13:21,020 --> 01:13:22,260
[SPEAKER_01] They just didn't want to say it.

850
01:13:22,260 --> 01:13:29,479
[SPEAKER_01] And I remember walking her to the back of, you know, the clinic to sit her down in the exam room.

851
01:13:29,479 --> 01:13:33,899
[SPEAKER_01] And I looked up to God and I thought, oh, why are you doing this to me?

852
01:13:33,899 --> 01:13:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] I'm about to leave.

853
01:13:35,279 --> 01:13:35,640
[SPEAKER_01] Why?

854
01:13:35,640 --> 01:13:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] You know, why are you doing this?

855
01:13:37,000 --> 01:13:39,640
[SPEAKER_01] And her pregnancy test was positive.

856
