[SPEAKER_01] And I went in the room and I congratulated her on her pregnancy.

857
01:13:43,659 --> 01:13:45,560
[SPEAKER_01] And she began to cry.

858
01:13:45,560 --> 01:13:51,100
[SPEAKER_01] And when she cried, I just looked at her and I said, what's, you know, what's wrong?

859
