860
01:13:53,819 --> 01:13:55,819
[SPEAKER_01] I think she was in her early 20s.

861
01:13:55,819 --> 01:13:59,899
[SPEAKER_01] And she had already had a daughter, a little girl.

862
01:13:59,899 --> 01:14:01,439
[SPEAKER_01] I think she was maybe three years old.

863
01:14:01,439 --> 01:14:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] And she said, I don't know if I can have this baby.

864
01:14:04,039 --> 01:14:07,840
