867
01:14:12,119 --> 01:14:17,939
[SPEAKER_01] And I don't know what I'm going to do if he gets out, you know, and I have this baby.

868
01:14:17,939 --> 01:14:21,539
[SPEAKER_01] And I don't know.

869
01:14:21,539 --> 01:14:24,199
[SPEAKER_01] I just connected with her on that.

870
01:14:25,000 --> 01:14:26,720
[SPEAKER_01] And I told her my story.

871
01:14:26,720 --> 01:14:33,859
