873
01:14:38,300 --> 01:14:40,500
[SPEAKER_01] And I just shared my own personal journey.

874
01:14:41,359 --> 01:14:45,600
[SPEAKER_01] And I asked her about her faith in God because she had a little cross on her neck.

875
01:14:45,600 --> 01:14:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] And she told me that, yes, she believed in God.

876
01:14:48,840 --> 01:14:58,060
[SPEAKER_01] And she didn't know that, you know, she was more concerned about what would happen with the father than, you know, she had her family support.

877
01:14:58,060 --> 01:14:59,880
